name: Two Rivers Public Health Department
tweet: Directed Health Measures impose limits on public gatherings and the magic number is 10 or less.  Businesses are not required to close at this time, i.e. salons, however every effort should be made to limit patrons present at one time.  Please RT to spread the word!

name: Two Rivers Public Health Department
tweet: A community-transmitted case of (COVID-19) was identified in Buffalo County. In coordination with the office of Governor Pete Ricketts, TRPHD will be enacting Directed Health Measures in Buffalo, Dawson, Franklin, Gosper, Harlan, Kearney, & Phelps Counties.
